    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response and a linear power band through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing kit, ensuring the chassis handles high-torque loads without compromise. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping and rebound characteristics, providing precise turn-in and mid-corner stability. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain and drivetrain remain mechanically sound and ready for spirited use.",
